title: SwifTEA: 4/30 Madness
description:
Why was April 30th suddenly a huge significance to the Swifties around the world? And why did it happen so fast? Nick, Lacey, Amy, and Ana discuss the madness from Swiftok in the last few days and share their feelings about this historic day in Swiftie history.
